MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 130

DECLARING CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN BARANGAY ILANG, BUNAWAN DISTRICT, DAVAO CITY AS SOCIALIZED HOUSING SITE FOR DISPOSITION TO BONAFIDE OCCUPANTS IN ACCORDANCE WITH REPUBLIC ACT NO. 730, IN RELATION TO THE PROVISIONS OF THE PUBLIC LAND ACT (C.A. NO. 141, AS AMENDED)

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO, President of the Philippines, do hereby declare certain parcels of public land situated in Brgy. Ilang, Bunawan District, Davao City as Socialized Housing Site for disposition to the actual occupants, in accordance with Republic Act No. 730, in relation to the provisions of the Public Land Act (Commonwealth Act No. 141, as amended). subject to private rights, if any there be, and to actual future survey. The subject parcels of land comprising a total area of 184,605 square meters, more or less, are more particularly described as follows:

FLC-(VIII-1)7

A PARCEL OF LAND (as shown on plan Flc-(VIII-1)7, L.R.C. Record No. ____), situated in the Barrio of Ilang, City of Davao. Bounded on the SW., along lines 1-2-3 by property of Bacnotan Cement Industries, Inc., (Flc-V-5311), on the NW., along lines 3-4-5 by Davao Gulf; and on the SE., along line 5-1 by property of Bacnotan Cement Industries, Inc. (Flc-V-5270).

Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan, being N. 66 deg. 29’E., 1033.81 m. from B.L.L.M. #8, Cad-102, Davao Cadastre;

91.13 m. to point 2;

522.25 m. to point 3;

215.18 m. to point 4;

611.09 m. to point 5;

210.10 m. to point of

beginning containing an area of ONE HUNDRED THIRTY FIVE THOUSAND TWO HUNDRED FORTY TWO (135,242) SQUARE METERS, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by B.L. cyl. conc. Mons.; bearings true; date of survey, January 9-10, 1970, which was approved, July 21, 1970.

FLC-V-5311

A PARCEL OF LAND (as shown on plan FLC-V-5311, L.R.C. Record No. ____), situated in the Barrio of Ilang, City of Davao. Bounded on the SE., along line 1-2 by Bacnotan Cement Industries, Inc. (FLC-V-5270), on the SW., along lines 2-3-4-5-6 by National Highway; on the NW., along line 6-7 by Davao Gulf; and on the NE., along lines 7-8-1 by Bacnotan Cement Industries, Inc. (FLC-[VIII-1])7.

