522.25 m. to point 8;

91.13 m to point of beginning

containing an area of FORTY NINE THOUSAND THREE HUNDRED SIXTY THREE (49,363) SQUARE METERS, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground as follows: point 2, by Old P.S. cyl. conc. Mons.; and the rest by B.L. cyl. conc. mons.; bearings true; date of survey, January 9-10, 1970, and was approved, July 21, 1970.

Such part or parts of the area herein declared open for disposition under R.A. 730, in relation to the provisions of the Public Land Act, as amended, which are being used or earmarked for public or quasi-public purposes shall be excluded from such disposition. Except in favor of the Government or any of its branches or agencies, all land disposed of under this proclamation shall not be subject to alienation and encumbrances for a period of ten (10) years from the issuance of title in case of sale, or execution of contract in case of lease, nor shall they become liable to the satisfaction of any debt contracted prior to the expiration of said period; but the improvements on the land may be mortgaged to qualified persons, associations or corporations.

An Inter-Agency Committee to be composed of the HUDCC, DENR, PCUP, NHA, City Government of Davao and concerned NGO/PO shall be created to formulate the guidelines for the disposition and implementation of a comprehensive housing plan for the area.

IN WITNESS THEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 5th day of December, in the year of Our Lord, two thousand and one.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

